blog.description: Semi-hiatus. They call me Tater. I recently divorced the Andi Mack canon, and remarried jyrus headcanon land where they did more with Jonah's anxiety, Marty never left the party, and jyrus is canon and also endgame.  Icon by cyrus-gayman.

title: 30 Days of Jyrus, Day 19
body:
My favorite jyrus quote is probably “you’re cool, man, can we leave it at that?” because in that moment Jonah automatically senses Cyrus’s anxiety, and cuts him off to clarify and repeat that he thinks highly of him. It’s one of many scenes that make a lot more sense in retrospect, now that Jonah is having panic attacks. Clearly, he’s been having anxiety for awhile, because he can recognize it in Cyrus. Plus, Jonah isn’t just saying that. He clearly means it.

And then from Cyrus’s perspective, he’s gone to all this effort to impress Jonah, and it turns out he didn’t have to. I think that’s maybe the first time that Cyrus sees that Jonah really cares about him, and you can tell how excited he is about it. (Cyrus deserves validation 2kforever).
